data.description: Nestled on a sprawling point lot with 115' of water frontage, this Pompano Beach gem dazzles with existing highlights and infinite possibilities. Featuring over 2,100 square feet of living area, this home is built for entertaining and enjoying the waterfront lifestyle. Experience the rare find of expansive, wide canal waterfront views throughout. Newer seawall/dock with boat lift (12,000 lbs) and floating dock. Interior highlights inside the three-bedroom, two-bath open layout include: Porcelain imported tile flooring; wide water views throughout the oversized living area; gourmet kitchen with Thermador appliances, custom cabinetry and quartz countertops; spa-inspired bathrooms; new AC unit and impact windows throughout.
